  ('medical-tech-moex-02835', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '身體發生感染或是嚴重發炎時，會誘發白血球上升，有時許多不成熟期白血球細胞也會出現在周邊血液，稱 之為類血癌反應（leukemoid reaction），此時需要與慢性骨髓性白血病（CML）做區分。在骨髓型態學檢查 中，下列何種發現比較會考慮是CML的病例？', '["有非典型巨核細胞（megakaryocytes）群聚", "LAP score上升", "無eosinophilia", "無basophilia"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "141dd4630ba7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fa2dcee952cb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-02836', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-113-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於顆粒球（granulocytes）發育過程各時期的特性，下列敘述何者錯誤？', '["Myeloblast是最早能由觀察型態分辨出的血球", "初級顆粒（primary granules) 最早在promyelocyte 時期出現", "特異性顆粒（specific granules）是從myelocyte時期開始出現", "自myelocyte時期開始，不再具有分裂增生的能力"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:14:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "141dd4630ba7", "answer_pdf_sha1": "fa2dcee952cb", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113020", "c": "308", "s": "22", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第一次專技人員高等考試醫師牙醫師中醫師藥師考試分階段考試、醫事檢驗師、醫事放射師、物理治療師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
